name: Bjd Dolls
description:
Focused on bjd dolls aesthetic, tested right on popular models (Deliberate, Hassan, Openjrny, etc.).
It can give a particular style for any character with a weight of 0.3/0.4

I spent time on this lora, you can buy me a coffee if you like it https://www.buymeacoffee.com/Hakaan911

  • Greatly helps in obtaining exotic colors for the iris. You can also test: iridescent, multicolor, shiny, mesmerizing eyes

  • For the hairs : disheveled, long, wavy, can give funs results

  • 768 res give better results

  • Turn off Restore faces and be gentle with negative prompts they aren't friendly with that anatomy !!
